OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBarge migrants' baptisms to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbe investigated            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Home Secretary is investigating how
OL,6, the asylum system deals with migrants  
OL,7, who have converted to Christianity.    
OL,9,FIt follows claims from a Weymouth      
OL,10,Fchurch that Muslim men living on board 
OL,11,Fthe Bibby Stockholm barge, which is    
OL,12,Fmoored off Portland in Dorset, were    
OL,13,Fpreparing for Christian baptism.       
OL,15,FSussex MP Tim Loughton raised the issue
OL,16,Fin Parliament on Wednesday.            
OL,18,FWeymouth Baptist Church insisted the   
OL,19,Frequests for baptism were genuine.     
